      "rationale": "An independent senior analyst reviewed all boundary condition assignments, material property inputs, and contact pair definitions against the ASTM F1717 fixture specification. Two discrepancies (incorrect friction coefficient on one contact pair) were identified and corrected prior to the validation runs. Final model was re-reviewed and approved."
